   	        <p>We at appeti.in believes in helping our customers as far as 							possible, and has therefore a liberal cancellation policy.</p>
                      <p>&nbsp; </p>
                      <p><strong>How do I cancel an order on appeti.in?</strong></p>
                      <p>If unfortunately you have to cancel an order, please email us at <a href="mailto:contact@appeti.in">contact@appeti.in</a><br>
                        For outright cancellations by you: </p>
                      <ul>
                        <li>If you cancel your order before your food items have 								been sourced, we will refund the entire amount.<br>
                        If the 								cancellation is after your food has shipped: </li>
                        <li>If you received the food, it will be eligible for 								exchange or refund only in case it is dis-satisfactory and the 								claim is genuine. The decision of <a href="http://www.appeti.in/refunds-cancellations/">Appeti.in</a> will be final in this case. </li>
            </ul>
                      <p>&nbsp; </p>
                      <p><strong>Refund Policy</strong></p>
            <p>Refunds will be made in 							the same method that the payment is received within 15 working 							days from the date of cancellation of order. </p>
            <p>&nbsp; </p>
            <p><strong>Return Policy</strong></p>
            <p>In case of complaints 							regarding foods that come with a warranty from Brand Owners, 							please refer the issue to the concerned Brand Owner. Let us know 							&amp; we'll help you regarding the same.</p>
            <p>If you think, 							you have received the food items in a bad condition or if the 							packaging is tampered with or damaged before delivery, please 							email us at <a href="mailto:contact@appeti.in">contact@appeti.in</a> mentioning your Order ID within 24 hours of accepting the 							package. We will request you for the pictures of the shipment and 							individual pictures of the boxes which will be provided to the 							Food Vendors and the courier partner within 48 hours of shipment 							delivery. If the claim is genuine as found by us, the Food Vendor 							and the Courier Partner, we will get the shipment picked back and 							initiate exchange or refund for the same.</p>
            <p><a href="http://www.appeti.in/refunds-cancellations/">Appeti.in</a> cannot offer refund 							for the following reasons<br>
            </p>
            <p>1) Shipment cannot be 							delivered because of the buyers unavailability.<br>
              2) 							Shipment cannot be delivered because of the wrong address.<br>
              3) Wrong orders placed by the customer and once the product is 							shipped.<br>
            4) User didn't intimate us in the mentioned 							time frame. </p>
